      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just feels so quiet now. i walk through the house and it’s like i’m a ghost. there’s no point in even making coffee or doing anything... he was the one who did all that. without him, i’m just staring at walls. i don't even know why i'm still getting up every morning.",
